featured_reviews.review_id: This is an old mosque built in early 19th century. After the establishment of modern Kamarhati Jutemill population of Kamarhati increased rapidly and few Mosques and temples build up in this area. The structure of this old mosque was damaged and since last two years it is under renovation. Inside the Mosque is already renovated and now it is looking beautiful, but outside of this mosque is not renovated yet due to fund crunch. After the evening prayer a madrassa school also running here.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Noori Jama Masjid In Kamarhatti.
It Is So Beautiful And Peaceful. I Was There Today (21st Ramadan)  In 'Khatam E Quraan'.
With Huzoor Sher E Bengal Al Haj Hazrat Allama Maulana Pir Mohammad Shamimuzzaman Qadri Al Hanafi.

This Year Taraweeh Is Been Performed By 'Alhaj Hafiz Hassan Mohammad' .
His Tongue Is Fast And Clear When He Read The Quraan E Paak  -  Mashallah Subahanallah

One Thing I Have Noticed That In Masjid 6 Ac's Are There But They Are Not Working..
I Feel Very Bad For This Because Weather Of There. It Was Too Hot.. 

The Imam Of There Is Very Good.
Name Of Imam Sahab - Allama Maulana Izhar Ashraf Qibla. By The Praise Of Allah Ta'ala, He Has One Boy And One Girl . His Name Is Zaid Ashraf And He Was So Fast And Too Cute. Masha Allah

In End I Wanna Say - Mashallah.

Team ZamaShamimi.
